  "text": "We obtain an interesting hybrid anisotropic/isotropic solid noise (Fig. 4(c) ) similarly but with ω i,φ = 0. A greater variety of solid noise patterns could be obtained by compositing solid noise patterns using widgets, as in [CITATION_1] ], or by using spatially varying solid noise parameters, as in [CITATION_2] ].",
